Weapon specialization has the ability to allow you to become very skilled
over time with a weapon type of your choice.  As time progresses, if you
stick to your weapon of choice you will begin to do more and more damage to
your opponents with each blow.  The downside to this of course is that
weapons in which you are not specialized you will not do quite as much
damage as a non-specialized person using the same weapon.  Many people
out there have chosen weapon specialization, so if you have additional
questions, it shouldn't be too difficult to find someone to talk to.

